from sklearn.pipeline import Pipeline
from sklearn.preprocessing import MinMaxScaler
from sklearn.feature_selection import SelectKBest,f_classif
models=[]
models.append(("RandomForest",Pipeline([("scaler",MinMaxScaler()),("feature selection",SelectKBest(score_func=f_classif)),("classifier",RandomForestClassifier())])))
models.append(("Naive Bayes",Pipeline([("scaler",MinMaxScaler()),("feature selection",SelectKBest(score_func=f_classif)),("classifier",GaussianNB())])))
models.append(("KNeighbors",Pipeline([("scaler",MinMaxScaler()),("feature selection",SelectKBest(score_func=f_classif)),("classifier",KNeighborsClassifier())])))
models.append(("SVM",Pipeline([("scaler",MinMaxScaler()),("feature selection",SelectKBest(score_func=f_classif)),("classifier",SVC(probability=True))])))
models.append(("AdaBoost",Pipeline([("scaler",MinMaxScaler()),("feature selection",SelectKBest(score_func=f_classif)),("classifier",AdaBoostClassifier())])))

for train,val in kfold.split(X,Y):
    X_tr = X.iloc[train]
    Y_tr = Y.iloc[train]
    X_val = X.iloc[val]
    Y_val = Y.iloc[val]
    j=0
    for name,model in models:
        model.fit(X_tr,Y_tr)
        pred=model.predict(X_val)
        if j==0:
            precision_RF.append(precision_score(Y_val,pred))
            recall_RF.append(recall_score(Y_val,pred))
            f1_RF.append(f1_score(Y_val,pred))
            accuracy_RF.append(accuracy_score(Y_val,pred))
            pred_proba=model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1]
            rocauc_RF.append(roc_auc_score(Y_val,pred_proba))
            overall_true_RF.extend(Y_val)
            overall_predict_RF.extend(pred)
            overall_predict_auc_RF.extend(pred_proba)
        elif j==1:
            precision_NB.append(precision_score(Y_val,pred))
            recall_NB.append(recall_score(Y_val,pred))
            f1_NB.append(f1_score(Y_val,pred))
            accuracy_NB.append(accuracy_score(Y_val,pred))
            pred_proba=model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1]
            rocauc_NB.append(roc_auc_score(Y_val,pred_proba))
            overall_true_NB.extend(Y_val)
            overall_predict_NB.extend(pred)
            overall_predict_auc_NB.extend(pred_proba)
        elif j==2:
            precision_KNN.append(precision_score(Y_val,pred))
            recall_KNN.append(recall_score(Y_val,pred))
            f1_KNN.append(f1_score(Y_val,pred))
            accuracy_KNN.append(accuracy_score(Y_val,pred))
            pred_proba=model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1]
            rocauc_KNN.append(roc_auc_score(Y_val,pred_proba))
            overall_true_KNN.extend(Y_val)
            overall_predict_KNN.extend(pred)
            overall_predict_auc_KNN.extend(pred_proba)
        elif j==3:
            precision_SVM.append(precision_score(Y_val,pred))
            recall_SVM.append(recall_score(Y_val,pred))
            f1_SVM.append(f1_score(Y_val,pred))
            accuracy_SVM.append(accuracy_score(Y_val,pred))
            pred_proba=model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1]
            rocauc_SVM.append(roc_auc_score(Y_val,pred_proba))
            overall_true_SVM.extend(Y_val)
            overall_predict_SVM.extend(pred)
            overall_predict_auc_SVM.extend(pred_proba)
        else:
            precision_ADA.append(precision_score(Y_val,pred))
            recall_ADA.append(recall_score(Y_val,pred))

            rocauc_ADA.append(roc_auc_score(Y_val,pred_proba))
            overall_true_ADA.extend(Y_val)
            overall_predict_ADA.extend(pred)
            overall_predict_auc_ADA.extend(pred_proba)
        j+=1

from imblearn.pipeline import Pipeline as ImbPipeline
models_resampled=[]
models_resampled.append(("RandomForest",ImbPipeline([("sampling",SMOTE(random_state=123)),("scaler",MinMaxScaler()),("feature selection",SelectKBest(score_func=f_classif)),("classifier",RandomForestClassifier())])))

Function that evaluates the models with SMOTE

In [ ]:
def eval_cross_validation(classifiers,skf,X,Y,model_res):
   
    accuracy_RF=[]
    accuracy_NB=[]
    accuracy_KNN=[]
    accuracy_SVM=[]
    accuracy_ADA=[]
    precision_RF=[]
    precision_NB=[]
    precision_KNN=[]
    precision_SVM=[]
    precision_ADA=[]
    recall_RF=[]
    recall_NB=[]
    recall_KNN=[]
    recall_SVM=[]
    recall_ADA=[]
    f1_RF=[]
    f1_NB=[]
    f1_KNN=[]
    f1_SVM=[]
    f1_ADA=[]
    rocauc_RF=[]
    rocauc_NB=[]
    rocauc_KNN=[]
    rocauc_SVM=[]
    rocauc_ADA=[]    
    overall_true_RF1=[]
    overall_predict_RF1=[]
    overall_predict_auc_RF1=[]    
    overall_true_NB1=[]
    overall_predict_NB1=[] 
    overall_predict_auc_NB1=[]   
    overall_true_KNN1=[]
    overall_predict_KNN1=[] 
    overall_predict_auc_KNN1=[]   
    overall_true_SVM1=[]
    overall_predict_SVM1=[] 
    overall_predict_auc_SVM1=[]   
    overall_true_ADA1=[]
    overall_predict_ADA1=[]
    overall_predict_auc_ADA1=[]  
    for train,val in skf.split(X,Y):
        X_tr = X.iloc[train]
        Y_tr = Y.iloc[train]
        X_val = X.iloc[val]
        Y_val = Y.iloc[val]
        j=0
        for name,model in classifiers:
            model.fit(X_tr,Y_tr)
            pred=model.predict(X_val)
            if j==0:
                precision_RF.append(precision_score(Y_val,pred))
                recall_RF.append(recall_score(Y_val,pred))
                f1_RF.append(f1_score(Y_val,pred))
                accuracy_RF.append(accuracy_score(Y_val,pred))
                pred_proba1=model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1]
                rocauc_RF.append(roc_auc_score(Y_val,pred_proba1))
                overall_true_RF1.extend(Y_val)
                overall_predict_RF1.extend(pred)
                overall_predict_auc_RF1.extend(pred_proba1)    
            elif j==1:
                pred_proba1=model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1]
                precision_NB.append(precision_score(Y_val,pred))
                recall_NB.append(recall_score(Y_val,pred))
                f1_NB.append(f1_score(Y_val,pred))
                accuracy_NB.append(accuracy_score(Y_val,pred))
                rocauc_NB.append(roc_auc_score(Y_val,pred_proba1))
                overall_true_NB1.extend(Y_val)
                overall_predict_NB1.extend(pred) 
                overall_predict_auc_NB1.extend(pred_proba1)    
            elif j==2:
                precision_KNN.append(precision_score(Y_val,pred))
                recall_KNN.append(recall_score(Y_val,pred))
                f1_KNN.append(f1_score(Y_val,pred))
                accuracy_KNN.append(accuracy_score(Y_val,pred))
                pred_proba1=model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1]
                rocauc_KNN.append(roc_auc_score(Y_val,pred_proba1))
                overall_true_KNN1.extend(Y_val)
                overall_predict_KNN1.extend(pred) 
                overall_predict_auc_KNN1.extend(pred_proba1)    
            elif j==3:
                precision_SVM.append(precision_score(Y_val,pred))
                recall_SVM.append(recall_score(Y_val,pred))
                f1_SVM.append(f1_score(Y_val,pred))
                accuracy_SVM.append(accuracy_score(Y_val,pred))
                pred_proba1=model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1]
                rocauc_SVM.append(roc_auc_score(Y_val,pred_proba1))
                overall_true_SVM1.extend(Y_val)
                overall_predict_SVM1.extend(pred) 
                overall_predict_auc_SVM1.extend(pred_proba1)    
            else:
                precision_ADA.append(precision_score(Y_val,pred))
                recall_ADA.append(recall_score(Y_val,pred))
                f1_ADA.append(f1_score(Y_val,pred))
                accuracy_ADA.append(accuracy_score(Y_val,pred))
                pred_proba1=model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1]
                rocauc_ADA.append(roc_auc_score(Y_val,pred_proba1))
                overall_true_ADA1.extend(Y_val)
                overall_predict_ADA1.extend(pred) 
                overall_predict_auc_ADA1.extend(pred_proba1)    
            j+=1  
        f1_AB2=np.array(f1_ADA)
        f1_RF2=np.array(f1_RF)
        f1_KNN2=np.array(f1_KNN)
        f1_SVM2=np.array(f1_SVM)
        f1_NB2=np.array(f1_NB)
    h=0
    for name,model in classifiers:
        if name=="RandomForest":
            model_res.loc[h]=[name,round(np.array(accuracy_RF).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(precision_RF).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(recall_RF).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(f1_RF).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(rocauc_RF).mean()*100,2)]
        elif name=="Naive Bayes":
            model_res.loc[h]=[name,round(np.array(accuracy_NB).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(precision_NB).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(recall_NB).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(f1_NB).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(rocauc_NB).mean()*100,2)]
        elif name=="KNeighbors":
            model_res.loc[h]=[name,round(np.array(accuracy_KNN).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(precision_KNN).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(recall_KNN).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(f1_KNN).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(rocauc_KNN).mean()*100,2)]
        elif name=="SVM":
            model_res.loc[h]=[name,round(np.array(accuracy_SVM).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(precision_SVM).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(recall_SVM).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(f1_SVM).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(rocauc_SVM).mean()*100,2)]
        else:
            model_res.loc[h]=[name,round(np.array(accuracy_ADA).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(precision_ADA).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(recall_ADA).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(f1_ADA).mean()*100,2),round(np.array(rocauc_ADA).mean()*100,2)]
        h+=1
    return model_res,f1_RF2,f1_NB2,f1_KNN2,f1_SVM2,f1_AB2,classifiers,overall_true_RF1,overall_predict_RF1,overall_true_NB1,overall_predict_NB1,overall_true_KNN1,overall_predict_KNN1,overall_true_SVM1,overall_predict_SVM1,overall_true_ADA1,overall_predict_ADA1,overall_predict_auc_RF1,overall_predict_auc_NB1,overall_predict_auc_KNN1,overall_predict_auc_SVM1,overall_predict_auc_ADA1
